sg":"<blockquote>雜誌引述消息人士指出，協議在於教區層面，以中國於1957年採用的「民主選舉」方式，由教區的神職人員、修女和教友代表一起投票選出候選人，再把名單給予北京當局，由他們通過外交途徑向梵蒂岡提交一名候選人的名字。教廷便將對該候選人進行調查，教宗根據調查結果批准或否決其任命。隨後，教廷再將他們的決定通知北京。<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/international/中梵或達協議-陳日君-完全是投降-對信仰的背叛-促教廷國務卿下台/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%E4%B8%AD%E6%A2%B5%E6%88%96%E9%81%94%E5%8D%94%E8%AD%B0-%E9%99%B3%E6%97%A5%E5%90%9B-%E5%AE%8C%E5%85%A8%E6%98%AF%E6%8A%95%E9%99%8D-%E5%B0%8D%E4%BF%A1%E4%BB%B0%E7%9A%84%E8%83%8C%E5%8F%9B-%E4%BF%83%E6%95%99%E5%BB%B7%E5%9C%8B%E5%8B%99%E5%8D%BF%E4%B8%8B%E5%8F%B0%2F&d=EzEu4lfYxXo0QcKw0PjQQUbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=3a91dfca\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%E4%B8%AD%E6%A2%B5%E6%88%96%E9%81%94%E5%8D%94%E8%AD%B0-%E9%99%B3%E6%97%A5%E5%90%9B-%E5%AE%8C%E5%85%A8%E6%98%AF%E6%8A%95%E9%99%8D-%E5%B0%8D%E4%BF%A1%E4%BB%B0%E7%9A%84%E8%83%8C%E5%8F%9B-%E4%BF%83%E6%95%99%E5%BB%B7%E5%9C%8B%E5%8B%99%E5%8D%BF%E4%B8%8B%E5%8F%B0%2F&h=0beaaf97\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/international/中梵或達協議-陳日君-完全是投降-對信仰的背叛-促教廷國務卿下台/</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌那聲，條儍鳩竟然仲信呢招<br />\n手中有權投票嘅，全部係中共嘅人<br />\n選乜人做主教已經可以預計到<br />\n睇下香港發生乜事都知到結果係點"},{"pid":"714de8a02e040eee7d4386e519d9c7bbcf2e3a2c","tid":830802,"uid":130105,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T16:11:33.000Z","msg":"好野，有生之年，重見幾樣歷史事件，今次就『禮儀之爭』，唔錯唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e3289fefa2ed3890c0ff2ef9da9664eea1ad0b0","tid":830802,"uid":79823,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T16:24:52.000Z","msg":"穌哥應該就嚟比佢激到落翻嚟"},{"pid":"43c9a9b0ab1f895b9a4be955cca22ed41be1ed40","tid":830802,"uid":121146,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201